date=2008-04-23&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.simonyi.ox.ac.uk%2Faims%2Findex.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASimonyi+Professor+for+the+Public+Understanding+of+Science\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/Richard_Dawkins\" title=\"Richard Dawkins\">Richard Dawkins</a>, \"Science, Genetics and Ethics: Memo for Tony Blair\", <i><a href=\"/wiki/A_Devil%27s_Chaplain\" title=\"A Devil&#39;s Chaplain\">A Devil's Chaplain</a></i>, Phoenix, 2003, page 43 (<a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-7538-1750-6\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-7538-1750-6\">978-0-7538-1750-6</a>).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20100526165723/http://www.simonyi.ox.ac.uk/previous-holders-simonyi-professorship/professor-richard-dawkins\">\"The Current Simonyi Professor: Richard Dawkins\"</a>. The University of Oxford. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.simonyi.ox.ac.uk/previous-holders-simonyi-professorship/professor-richard-dawkins\">the original</a> on 26 May 2010<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 March</span> 2008</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Current+Simonyi+Professor%3A+Richard+Dawkins&amp;rft.pub=The+University+of+Oxford&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.simonyi.ox.ac.uk%2Fprevious-holders-simonyi-professorship%2Fprofessor-richard-dawkins&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASimonyi+Professor+for+the+Public+Understanding+of+Science\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Richard Dawkins. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.richarddawkins.net/article,2246,Charles-Simonyi-Professorship-in-the-Public-Understanding-of-Science,Richard-Dawkins\">\"Charles Simonyi Professorship in the Public Understanding of Science\"</a>. RichardDawkins.net<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-03-29</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Charles+Simonyi+Professorship+in+the+Public+Understanding+of+Science&amp;rft.pub=RichardDawkins.net&amp;rft.au=Richard+Dawkins&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.richarddawkins.net%2Farticle%2C2246%2CCharles-Simonyi-Professorship-in-the-Public-Understanding-of-Science%2CRichard-Dawkins&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASimonyi+Professor+for+the+Public+Understanding+of+Science\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/Richard_Dawkins\" title=\"Richard Dawkins\">Richard Dawkins</a>, <i><a href=\"/wiki/Brief_Candle_in_the_Dark:_My_Life_in_Science\" title=\"Brief Candle in the Dark: My Life in Science\">Brief Candle in the Dark: My Life in Science</a></i>, <a href=\"/wiki/Bantam_Press\" title=\"Bantam Press\">Bantam Press</a>, 2015, page 282 (<a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-59307-256-1\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-59307-256-1\">978-0-5930